{
    "text": "Modern Soho Sri Lankan restaurant @kolamba.ldn gets \u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50 from Time Out's Food Editor Tania Ballantine: \"From the kitchen, there were flashes of brilliance like the fish cutlets \u2013 aka spiced mini fishcakes with deep-fried coats \u2013 that were good enough to rival my dad\u2019s (which are legendary). Best of all: the creamy and comforting cucumber curry. You Must Get This. (At \u00a35.90, it\u2019s also a steal.) Hoppers were decent, string hoppers \u2013 that rarest of steamed delights \u2013 even better.\" Follow our link in bio for all the info.",
